{"tid":2238992,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"就是愛台灣！AV女優苦學中文就想嫁台男…已聽懂7成中文","createTime":"2020-10-11T14:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T06:16:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8a9d5be36553139a22663e16774cae024c744b","tid":2238992,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:28:10.000Z","msg":"32歲的日本前AV女優乃乃果花（乃々果花），在踏入成人產業前曾用「石川惠理」名字以女偶像出道紅極一時。這幾年來更多次在推特提及「喜歡台灣、想來台灣工作」近期爆出最新消息，在疫情趨緩控制後，極有可能來台工作引發話題！<br />\n<br />\n上圍豐滿的乃乃果花，在AV女優活耀期間知名度不亞於她在偶像時期，受到許多粉絲們喜愛，甚至一路紅到台灣來，而在2016年正式宣布引退時，也讓不少網友十分扼腕與可惜。<br />\n<br />\n所幸她仍活耀於社群平台，不時粉絲們還能接收到她的生活點滴，而與她工作上常接觸的暗黑界權威一劍浣春秋也透露，過去在2016年來台時，她就被一個身穿鋼鐵人衣服的男生「煞到」，甚至於還廣為詢問該男下落，甚至認為對方就是天菜，加深她對台灣的好感度！<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋也透漏，乃乃果花私下多次來台，還曾直言：「沒有比我更愛台灣的女優了」近來他與乃乃果花的書信中文大幅度進展，大約7成以上中文語意都看得懂。近來他與乃乃果花溝通工作時對方驚喜宣布，自己將安排定居台灣，未來希望以成為偶像劇演員為目標。倘若真的成功台來定居，與台男結婚也是相當有可能的事情。"},{"pid":"5ddc302e55868937f842f68ce4dc897888aa0db4","tid":2238992,"uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/11/2820857-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F2820857-PH.jpg&h=ecfefd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲前AV女優乃乃果花多次表明超愛台灣。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/11/2820864-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F2820864-PH.jpg&h=0282499b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲乃乃果花2016年引退讓粉絲哀鴻遍野。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/11/2820867-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F11%2F2820867-PH.jpg&h=9b602f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲一劍浣春秋公布兩人對話確定她來台消息。（圖／翻攝自一劍浣春秋部落格）"},{"pid":"79fef9151a707d7346afa4acce5d3f1478a53efb","tid":2238992,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0cf0e313569f844158162e9db93132b27154ad","tid":2238992,"uid":378305,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"揾人埋單"},{"pid":"7df4e8915ebe3204d598f3fc3207ee98f1020c17","tid":2238992,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"都唔少日本女優 靚女<br />\n想去台灣"},{"pid":"1ee81ba5fc34d2931bacad74d92df91998406d65","tid":2238992,"uid":8410,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"32 歲攻台有難度， 本身台灣都唔少靚女"},{"pid":"7dcb00718f7f7f574a6f72bebf9ff24beea65e26","tid":2238992,"uid":16659,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"5a0cf0e313569f844158162e9db93132b27154ad","tid":2238992,"uid":378305,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"揾人埋單"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tva2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0080fUcAgy1ghkq4i811ug30b807vx6t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftva2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0080fUcAgy1ghkq4i811ug30b807vx6t.gif&h=9e6cb0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tva2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0080fUcAgy1ghkq4nwtwxg30b807vb2f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftva2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0080fUcAgy1ghkq4nwtwxg30b807vb2f.gif&h=52cd02dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5df36970b8eb49d56efdb20521a02381bbfe5ea8","tid":2238992,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffdade78f12b0a7c82724ca4c35b63bb41dccaf7","tid":2238992,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"樓上what name"},{"pid":"f7faa636416fc1c1ef04865ae3342efe075347bc","tid":2238992,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s